title: 140 [Rhythmic Game]
description:
Only for windows. Comment if you want the linux or Mac version and I'll upload it!

Enjoy and support the developers.

"140 is a masterful, mentally stimulating platformer with a distinct visual and aural style" 8/10 - IGN

"140 is a magnetically moreish experience: delicately balanced and well thought-out." 8/10 - Edge

The game was developed by:

Jeppe Carlsen (design and programming),
Jakob Schmid (audio),
Niels Fyrst and Andreas Peitersen (visual concept).

The game won the IGF 2013 award for Excellence in Audio, and got honorable mention in Technical Excellence
